# Synopsis    : Mock ss binary for testing
# Description : Simulates ss output for port availability checks.
#               Returns a header-only (no listeners) line by default.
# Notes       : Set SS_MOCK_OUTPUT to inject listener rows so a test can
#               exercise the port-in-use path.
